description: Add (a Time Tracer) is trying to steal Eve (as a Code: Exotic)’s core for his own use but was found out by Eun. Much to his surprise, Eun offers Add help with stealing Eve’s core. Though there seem to be other reasons behind Eun’s support, Add still decides to let the fox help.>
